item.title: Models in Artificial Intelligence
item.description: Model is a simplified version of a real world entity that focuses on some of the properties of the real object that are under study. Similar to the models doing a ramp walk, help us understand how the clothes developed by a designer might look, models are an integral part of software industry, that help in catering to a specific set of properties that we want to create in the soft world.
